D E _ E L I I T T I S A U N A

By NakkiMaisteri

OBJECTIVE

Terrorists: Plant the bomb to the sauna located in middle of the map.!
Counter terrorists: Protect the sauna from demolition by all cost!

MAP INFORMATION

Map has special "spawn area" where all players have 60 seconds to choose their "class" and buy their gear, if the time expires and the player is still at spawn area, the player will die.

Classes are: 
1. Speed: + Minor speed, - Minor damage
2. Recon: + Major Invisibility, - Major damage
3. Heavy: + Heavy machinegun, - Minor speed
If you don't wish to have a class you can just walk forward to the pit and have default stats.

Whole map is completely symmetrical.
Map doesn't have light sources, since this map's gonna be more about performance than looking good.

Map contains: "Single bomb site / "Class" system / High FPS" Recommented players/Max players: 24/34 
Spawnpoints: Both teams will spawn next to each other in a "Spawn area".
All of the map isn't in the screenshots, EXPLORE!

Download --> Test --> Comment --> Rate.

Kittehs will thank you!
